title: War of the Roses: He Was Sending His Ex a Letter
description: Cal is concerned something is going on with his boyfriend Anthony, and Anthony's ex-fiance.  Cal recently found something in the mail that Anthony was sending to his ex and he's noticed Anthony taking cash out a lot.  We switch things up this week for a "couples" outing to see who Anthony wants to do it with!
